prefs
Class VSPrefs

java.lang.Object
  prefs.VSPrefs
Direct Known Subclasses:
VSMessage, VSSerializablePrefs
public class VSPrefs
extends java.lang.Object

The class VSPrefs, this class is for dynamic data storage. It can hold various different types such as Boolean, Floats, Integers, Strings, Colors.

Author:
Paul C. Buetow
